{"tid":1723054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請勿放棄思考 阻放工必然為假行動","createTime":"2019-11-15T05:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:28:19.000Z","uid":36104,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"af27cd7bef5cc09d84391f943cbdcd812718144c","tid":1723054,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"運動中精神緊張、面對惡劣環境<br />\n連登又遭大量入侵及風向撚<br />\n<br />\n請保持冷靜及持續思考<br />\n可能諗完都會中伏被帶風向<br />\n錯唔緊要<br />\n努力唔好錯下一次<br />\n<br />\n例如咩阻人放工<br />\n一諗都知冇目標<br />\n阻返工係為左幫人罷工、留人喺屋企<br />\n阻放工人地瞓公司、遲返屋企<br />\n同罷工目標背道而馳<br />\n<br />\n又例如狂屌大學海關post<br />\n屌係冇用<br />\n溝通先有用<br />\n我地唔係支那、支港<br />\n我地係識得協商<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多巴打棄左lihkg、只用tg<br />\n但有睇嘅巴打請持續思考，請勿放棄用腦"},{"pid":"06456a51a8132335e4d6e12f6c5b167dfd7a5ba9","tid":1723054,"uid":36104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"請勿放棄思考<br />\n我地唔係冇腦偽進"},{"pid":"fddb4b2ade5c38cec215e19b1efcca94784c97a0","tid":1723054,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"明顯係<br />\n放心我見手足都唔打算理"},{"pid":"28465898c048f12b2700d08c281195d2471c05d8","tid":1723054,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"請勿放棄思考<br />\n我地唔係冇腦偽進"},{"pid":"b9d80b2d0acc6db1eff0f3b011276b655223ada4","tid":1723054,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbf67236b31c2059d7e49c39bd245598a819a6d3","tid":1723054,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"做多咗啦班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe4152ced3a14adc2025321b2332aa3e01d4a29","tid":1723054,"uid":156771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfa49670bc7a56cf6a1052ca80225bf96ec79310","tid":1723054,"uid":36104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply